# Developer Agent Context Summary

## Last Run: 2026-03-14

## Completed Work This Session

### collate: SortedDict iteration fix (Task #424)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/collate

Added `__iter__` and `__reversed__` overrides to SortedDict that delegate to `self._keys`. Previously inherited from dict, returning insertion order. 6 new tests added. 218 tests pass. CI green.

### slugsmith: Accented Greek/Cyrillic transliteration fix (Task #425)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/slugsmith

NFKD fallback in `transliterate()` now strips combining marks (Mn/Mc) and re-checks base characters against CHAR_MAP, instead of `.encode("ascii", "ignore")` which dropped non-Latin base chars. All 7 accented Greek letters now work. 9 new tests, 96 total pass.

### slugsmith: Type annotation widening + minor fixes (Task #426)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/slugsmith

- `stopwords`: `tuple[str, ...]` → `Iterable[str]`
- `replacements`: `list[tuple[str, str]]` → `Sequence[Sequence[str]]`
- Pre-compiled `_UNICODE_ALLOWED_RE` for `allow_unicode` path
- Documented `save_order` as compat-only (always preserves order)
- 96 tests pass, mypy clean.

